quran[357]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Iske baad uski qaum par humne aasmaan se koi lashkar nahin utara , humein lashkar bhejne ki koi haajat na thi"
  36,29,Bas ek dhamaka hua aur yakayak woh sab bujh kar reh gaye
  36,30,"Afsos bandon ke haal par, jo Rasool bhi unke paas aaya uska woh mazaaq hi udatey rahey"
  36,31,Kya unhon ne dekha nahin ke unsey pehle kitni hi qaumon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain aur iske baad woh phir kabhi unki taraf palat kar na aaye
  36,32,Un sab ko ek roz hamare saamne haazir kiya jaana hai
  36,33,"In logon ke liye be-jaan zameen ek nishani hai, humne isko zindagi bakshi aur issey galla (anaaj / grain) nikala jisey yeh khaate hain"
  36,34,Humne ismein khajuron aur angooron ke baagh paida kiye aur uske andar chashme (springs) phodh nikale
  36,35,"Taa-ke yeh uske phal khayein, yeh sab kuch inke apne haathon ka paida kiya hua nahin hai phir kya yeh shukar ada nahin karte"
  36,36,Paak hai woh zaat jisne jumla aqsaam ke joday paida kiye khwah woh zameen ki nabataat mein se hon ya khud inki apni jins (yani naw-e-Insani) mein se ya un ashyah mein se jinko yeh jaante tak nahin hain
  36,37,"Inke liye ek aur nishani raat hai, hum uske upar se din hata dete hain to inpar andhera chaa jata hai"
  36,38,"Aur Suraj, woh apne thikane ki taraf chala ja raha hai, yeh zabardat aleem(All-Knowing) hasti ka bandha hua hisaab hai"
  36,39,"Aur chand, uske liye humne manzilein muqarrar kardi hain yahan tak ke insey guzarta hua woh phir khajur ki sukhi shaakh (dry old branch) ke manind reh jata hai"
  36,40,Na Suraj ke bas mein yeh hai ke woh chand ko ja pakde aur na raat din par sabqat le ja sakti hai. Sab ek ek falak mein tair rahey hain
  36,41,Inke liye yeh bhi ek nishani hai ke humne inki nasal ko bhari hui kashti mein sawaar kardiya
  36,42,Aur phir inke liye waisi hi kashtiyan aur paida ki jinpar yeh sawaar hotay hain
  36,43,"Hum chahein to inko garq kardein, koi inki fariyad sunne wala na ho aur kisi tarah yeh na bachaye jaa sakein"
  36,44,Bas hamari rehmat hi hai jo inhein paar lagati aur ek waqt e khaas tak zindagi se mutamatta (enjoyment) honay ka mauqa deti hai
  36,45,"In logon se jab kaha jaata hai ke bacho us anjaam se jo tumhare aagey aa raha hai aur tumhare peechey guzar chukka hai, shayad ke tumpar reham kiya jaye (to yeh suni an suni kar jatey hain)"
  36,46,Inke saamne inke Rubb ki aayat(nishani) mein se jo aayat(nishani) bhi aati hai yeh iski taraf iltifaat nahin karte
  36,47,Aur jab insey kaha jaata hai ke Allah ne jo rizq tumhein ata kiya hai usmein se kuch Allah ki raah mein bhi kharch karo to yeh log jinhon ne kufr kiya hai iman laney walon ko jawab dete hain “ kya hum unko khilayein jinhein agar Allah chahta to khud khila deta? Tum to bilkul hi behak gaye ho”
  36,48,Yeh log kehte hain ke “yeh qayamat ki dhamki aakhir kab poori hogi? Batao agar tum sacche ho”
  36,49,Dar-asal yeh jis cheez ki raah takk rahey hain woh bas ek dhamaka hai jo yakayak inhein ain us halat mein dhar lega jab yeh (apne dunyavi maamlaat mein) jhagad rahey hongey
  36,50,"Aur us waqt yeh wasiyat tak na kar sakenge, na apne gharon ko palat sakenge"
  36,51,Phir ek soor (trumpet) phoonka jayega aur yakayak ye apne Rubb ke huzur pesh honay ke liye apni qabaron se nikal padenge
  36,52,"Ghabra kar kahenge : “Arey, yeh kisne humein hamari khwab-gaah se utha khada kiya?” Yeh wahi cheez hai jiska khuda e rehman ne wada kiya tha aur Rasoolon ki baat sacchi thi”"
  36,53,Ek hi zoar ki aawaz hogi aur sab ke sab hamare saamne haazir kardiye jayenge
  36,54,Aaj kisi par zarra barabar zulm na kiya jayega aur tumhein waisa hi badla diya jayega jaise amal tum karte rahe thay
  36,55,Aaj jannati log mazey karne mein mashgul hain
  36,56,Woh aur unki biwiyan ghanay saayon (shades) mein hain masnadon par takiye lagaye huey
  36,57,"Har qisam ki lazeez cheezein khane peene ko unke liye wahan maujood hain, jo kuch woh talab karein unke liye haazir hai"
  36,58,Rubb e Raheem ki taraf se unko salaam kaha gaya hai
  36,59,"Aur aey mujrimon, aaj tum chatt kar alag ho jao"
  36,60,"Adam ke bacchon, kya maine tumko hidayat na ki thai ke shaytaan ki bandagi na karo, woh tumhara khula dushman hai"
  36,61,"Aur meri hi bandagi karo, yeh seedha raasta hai"
  36,62,"Magar iske bawajood usne tum mein se ek giroh-e-kaseer (great multitude of you) ko gumraah kardiya, kya tum aqal nahin rakhte thay"
  36,63,Yeh wahi jahannum hai jissey tumko daraya jata raha tha
  36,64,Jo kufr tum duniya mein karte rahey ho uski padaish mein ab iska indhan (fuel) bano
  36,65,"Aaj hum inke mooh bandh kiye detey hain, inke haath humse bolenge aur inke paon gawahi denge ke yeh duniya mein kya kamayi karte rahey hain"
  36,66,"Hum chahein to inki aankhein moond dein(obliterated their eyes), phir yeh raastey ki taraf lapak kar dekhein, kahan se inhein raasta sujhayi dega"
  36,67,Hum chahein to inhein inki jagah hi par is taraf maskh (transform) karke rakh dein ke yeh na aagey chal sakein na peechey palat sakein
  36,68,"Jis shaks ko hum lambi umar dete hain iski saakht ko hum ulat hi dete hain (we reverse in creation), kya (yeh halaat dekh kar) inhein aqal nahin aati"
  36,69,"Humne is (Nabi) ko sher nahin sikhaya hai aur na shayari isko zeib hi deti hai, yeh to ek naseehat hai aur saaf padhi janey wali kitaab"
  36,70,Taa-ke woh har us shaks ko khabardar karde jo zinda ho aur inkar karne walon par hujjat qayam ho jaye
  36,71,Kya yeh log dekhte nahin hain ke humne apne haathon ki banayi hui cheezon mein se inke liye maweshi paida kiye aur ab yeh inke maalik hain
  36,72,"Humne unhein is tarah inke bas mein kardiya hai ke unmein se kisi par yeh sawaar hotey hain, kisika yeh gosht khate hain"
  36,73,Aur unke andar inke liye tarah tarah ke fawaid (benefits) aur mashrubaat (drinks) hain phir kya yeh shukar guzar nahin hotay
  36,74,Yeh sabkuch hotey huey inhon ne Allah ke siwa dusre khuda bana liye hain aur yeh umeed rakhte hain ke inki madad ki jayegi
  36,75,Woh inki koi madad nahin kar sakte balke yeh log ultey unke liye hazir-baash lashkar (army in waiting ) baney huey hain
  36,76,"Accha, jo baatein yeh bana rahey hain woh tumhein ranjeeda na karein, inki chupi aur khuli sab baaton ko hum jaante hain"
  36,77,Kya Insaan dekhta nahin hai ke humne usey nutfe(sperm drop) se paida kiya aur phir woh sareeh jhagdalu bankar khada ho gaya
  36,78,"Ab woh humpar misalein chaspan karta hai aur apni paidaish ko bhool jaata hai , kehta hai “kaun in haddiyon ko zinda karega jabke yeh boseeda (rotten) ho chuki hon?”"
  36,79,"Ussey kaho,inhein wahi zinda karega jisne pehle inhein paida kiya tha, aur woh takhleeq (creation) ka har kaam jaanta hai"
  36,80,Wahi jisne tumhare liye harey bharey (green) darakht se aag paida kardi aur tum ussey apne chuleh (stoves) roshan karte ho
  36,81,"Kya woh jisne aasmaano aur zameen ko paida kiya ispar qadir nahin hai ke in jaison ko paida kar sakey? Kyun nahin, jabke woh maahir khallaq (superb creator) hai"
  36,82,Woh to jab kisi cheez ka irada karta hai to uska kaam bas yeh hai ke usey hukum de ke hoja aur woh jo jati hai
  36,83,"Paak hai woh jiske haath mein har cheez ka mukammal iqtedar (full control) hai, aur usi ki taraf tum paltaye janey waale ho"
  37,1,Qataar dar qataar saff baandhne walon ki kasam
  37,2,Phir unki kasam jo daatne phatkaar ne waley hain
  37,3,Phir unki kasam jo kalaam e naseehat sunane waley hain
  37,4,Tumhara mabood e haqiqi bas ek hi hai
  37,5,"Woh jo zameen aur aasmaano ka aur tamaam un cheezon ka maalik hai jo zameen o aasmaan mein hain, aur saarey mashrikon(easts) ka maalik"
  37,6,Humne aasmaan e duniya ko taaron ki zeenat se aarasta (adorn) kiya hai
  37,7,Aur har shaytan sarkash se isko mehfooz kardiya hai
  37,8,"Yeh shayateen mala-e-aala (High Council) ki baatein nahin sun saktey, har taraf se maarey aur haankey jatey hain"
  37,9,Aur inke liye paiham azaaab hai
  37,10,Taaham agar koi inmein se kuch ley uday to ek teiz shola uska peecha karta hai
  37,11,"Ab insey pucho, inki paidaish zyada mushkil hai ya un cheezon ki jo humne paida kar rakkhi hain? Inko to humne leis daar gaaray(sticky clay/chickni mitti) se paida kiya hai"
  37,12,Tum (Allah ki qudrat ke karishmon par) hairan ho aur yeh iska mazaak uda rahey hain
  37,13,Samjhaya jaata hai to samajh kar nahin detey
  37,14,Koi nishani dekhte hain to usey thatton (mazaak/mock) mein udatey hain
  37,15,Aur kehte hain “ yeh to sareeh jaadu hai
  37,16,Bhala kahin aisa ho sakta hai ke jab hum mar chuke hon aur mitti ban jayein aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jaye us waqt hum phir zinda karke utha khade kiye jayein
  37,17,Aur kya hamare agle waqton ke aaba o ajdaad bhi uthaye jayenge?”
  37,18,"(insey kaho haan, aur tum) khuda ke muqable mein baybas ho"
  37,19,Bas ek hi jhidki hogi aur yakayak yeh apni aankhon se (woh sab kuch jiski khabar di jaa rahi hai) dekh rahey hongey
  37,20,"Us waqt yeh kahengey “ haaye hamari kambakhti , yeh to yaum ul jaza hai”"
  37,21,“yeh wahi faisley ka din hai jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay”
  37,22,(Hukum hoga) gher lao sab zaalimon aur unke saathiyon aur un maboodon ko jinki woh khuda ko chodh kar bandagi kiya karte thay
  37,23,Phir un sab ko jahannum ka raasta dikhao
  37,24,"Aur zara inhein thehrao, inse kuch puchna hai"
  37,25,"“Kya ho gaya tumhein, ab kyun ek dusre ki madad nahin karte"
  37,26,"(Arey, aaj to yeh apne aap ko) aur ek dusre ko hawaliye (surrender) kiye de rahe hain”"
  37,27,Iske baad yeh ek dusre ki taraf mudenge aur baham takrar shuru kar dengey
  37,28,"pairvi karne waley apne peshwaon[leaders] se) kahenge, “Tum hamare paas seedhay rukh se aate thay”"
  37,29,Woh jawaab dengey “nahin balke tum khud iman laney waley na thay
  37,30,"Hamara tumpar koi zoar na tha, tum khud hi sarkash log thay"
  37,31,Aakhir e kaar hum apne Rubb ke is farmaan ke mustahiq ho gaye ke hum azaab ka maza chakhne waley hain
  37,32,"So humne tumko behkaya, hum khud behke huye thay”"
  37,33,Is taraah woh sab us roz azaab mein mushtarik (shareek) hongey
  37,34,Hum mujreemon ke saath yahi kuch kiya karte hain
  37,35,Yeh woh log thay ke jab unsey kaha jata “Allah ke siwa koi maabood e barhaqq nahin hai” to yeh ghamand mein aa jatey thay
  37,36,Aur kehte thay “kya hum ek shayar majnoon (dewane) ki khaatir apne maboodon ko chodh dein?”
  37,37,Halaanke woh haqq lekar aaya tha aur usne Rasoolon ki tasdeeq ki thi
  37,38,(Ab unse kaha jayega ke) tum laaziman dardnaak saza ka maza chakhne waley ho
  37,39,Aur tumhein jo badla bhi diya jaa raha hai unhi aamaal ka diya ja raha hai jo tum karte rahey ho
  37,40,Magar Allah ke cheeda (chune huey/chosen) banday (is anjaam e badd se) mehfooz hongey
  37,41,Unke liye jaana bujha rizq (known provision) hai
  37,42,Har tarah ki lazeez cheezein
  37,43,Aur niyamat bhari jannatein
  37,44,"Jinmein woh izzat ke saath rakkhey jayenge, takhaton par aamne saamne baithenge"
  37,45,Sharaab ke chamson (springs) se sagar (cups) bhar bhar kar unke darmiyan phiraye jayenge
  37,46,"Chamakti hui sharaab, jo peene waalon ke liye lazzat hogi"
  37,47,Na unke jism ko ussey koi zarar hoga aur na unki aqal ussey kharab hogi
  37,48,"Aur unke paas nigahein bachane wali, khoobsurat aankhon wali auratein hongi"
  37,49,Aisi naazuk jaise andey (egg) ke chilke ke nichey chupi hui jhilli
  37,50,Phir woh ek dusre ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar halaat puchengey
  37,51,"Unmein se ek kahega, “duniya mein mera ek hum nahseen (companion) tha"
  37,52,"Jo mujhse kaha karta tha, kya tum bhi tasdeeq karne walon mein se ho"
  37,53,Kya waqayi jab hum mar chuke hongey aur mitti ho jayenge aur haddiyon ka panjar bankar reh jayenge to humein jaza o saza di jayegi
  37,54,Ab kya aap log dekhna chahte hain ke woh sahib ab kahan hain?”
  37,55,Yeh keh kar junhi woh jhukega to jahannum ki gehrayi mein usko dekh lega
  37,56,"Aur ussey khitaab karke kahega “khuda ki kasam, tu to mujhey tabaah hi kar dene wala tha"
  37,57,Mere Rubb ka fazal shamil e haal na hota to aaj main bhi un logon mein se hota jo pakde huey aaye hain
  37,58,Accha to kya ab hum marne waley nahin hain
  37,59,Maut jo humein aani thi woh bas pehle aa chuki? Ab humein koi azaab nahin hona?”
  37,60,Yakeenan yahi azeem o shaan kaamiyabi hai
  37,61,Aisi hi kamiyabi ke liye amal karne walon ko amal karna chahiye
  37,62,"Bolo, yeh ziyafat acchi hai ya zakkhum ka darakht"
  37,63,Humne us darakht ko zaalimon ke liye fitna bana diya hai
  37,64,Woh ek darakht hai jo jahannum ki teh se nikalta hai
  37,65,Uske shagufe (emerging fruit) aise hain jaise shaytano ke sar
  37,66,Jahannum ke log usey khayenge aur usi se pait bharengey
  37,67,Phir ispar peene ke liye khaulta hua pani milega
  37,68,Aur iske baad unki wapsi usi aatish e dozakh (blazing Hell) ki taraf hogi
  37,69,Yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne baap dada ko gumraah paya
  37,70,Aur unhi ke nakshe qadam par daud chale
  37,71,Halaanke unse pehle bahut se log gumraah ho chuke thay
  37,72,Aur unmein humne tambeeh (warn) karne walay Rasool bheje thay
  37,73,Ab dekhlo ke un tambeeh kiye janey walon ka kya anjaam hua
  37,74,Is bad-anjaami se bas Allah ke wahi banday bachay hain jinhein usne apne liye khalis karliya hai
  37,75,"Humko (issey pehle) Nooh ne pukara tha, to dekho ke hum kaise acche jawab dene waley thay"
  37,76,Humne usko aur uske ghar walon ko karb-e-azeem (badi musibat) se bacha liya
  37,77,Aur usi ki nasal ko baaki rakkha
  37,78,Aur baad ki nasalon mein iski taarif o tausif chodh di
  37,79,Salaam hai Nooh par tamaam duniya walon mein
  37,80,Hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza diya karte hain
  37,81,Dar haqeeqat woh hamare momin bandon mein se tha
  37,82,Phir dusre giroh ko humne garq (drown) kardiya
  37,83,Aur Nooh hi ke tareeqey par chalne wala Ibrahim tha
  37,84,Jab woh apne Rubb ke huzur qalb e saleem lekar aaya
  37,85,Jab usne apne baap aur apni qaum se kaha “yeh kya cheezein hain jinki tum ibadat kar rahey ho
  37,86,Kya Allah ko chodh kar jhoot ghadey huey maabood chahte ho
  37,87,Aakhir Allah Rubb-ul-Aalameen ke baarey mein tumhara kya gumaan hai?”
  37,88,Phir usne taaron par ek nigaah daali
  37,89,Aur kaha meri tabiyat kharaab hai
  37,90,Chunanche woh log usey chodh kar chale gaye
  37,91,Unke peechey woh chupke se unke maboodon ke mandir mein ghus gaya aur bola “aap log khate kyun nahin hain
  37,92,"Kya ho gaya, aap log bolte bhi nahin?”"
  37,93,Iske baad woh unpar pil (toot) pada aur seedhay haath se khoob zarbein lagayi (todhna shuru kiya)
  37,94,(Wapas aakar) woh log bhaage bhaage uske paas aaye
  37,95,Usne kaha “kya tum apni hi tarashi hui cheezon ko poojhte ho
  37,96,Halaanke Allah hi ne tumko bhi paida kiya hai aur un cheezon ko bhi jinhein tum banatey ho”
  37,97,Unhon ne aapas mein kaha “ iske liya ek alaaw (pyre) tayyar karo aur isey dehakti hui aag ke dhair mein phenk do”
  37,98,"Unhon ne uske khilaf ek karawayi karna chahi thi, magar humne unhi ko nicha dikha diya"
  37,99,"Ibrahim ne kaha “ main apne Rubb ki taraf jata hoon, wahi meri rehnumayi karega"
  37,100,"Aey parwardigar , mujhey ek beta ata kar jo salihon (righteous) mein se ho”"
  37,101,(Is dua ke jawab mein)humne usko ek haleem (burdbaar) ladke ki basharat di
  37,102,"Woh ladka jab uske saath daud dhoop karne ki umar ko pahunch gaya to ( ek roz) Ibrahim ne ussey kaha, “beta, main khwab mein dekhta hoon ke main tujhey zibaah kar raha hoon, ab tu bata, tera kya khayal hai?” usne kaha, “abbajan , jo kuch aapko hukum diya jaa raha hai usey kar daliye, aap insha Allah mujhey saabiron(sabr karne walon) mein se payenge”"
  37,103,Aakhir ko jab in dono ne sar-e-tasleem kham kardiya aur Ibrahim ne bete ko maathay ke bal gira diya
  37,104,Aur humne nida di ke “Aey Ibrahim
  37,105,Tu nay khwab sach kar dikhaya hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza deta hain
  37,106,Yaqeenan yeh ek khuli aazmaaish thi”
  37,107,Aur humne ek badi qurbani fidiye mein de kar us bacchey ko chuda liya
  37,108,Aur uski taarif o tauseef hamesha ke liye baad ki nasalon mein chodh di
  37,109,Salaam hai Ibrahim par
  37,110,Hum neki karne waalon ko aisi hi jaza detay hain
  37,111,Yaqeenan woh hamare momin bandon mein se tha
  37,112,"Aur humne usey Ishaq(Issac) ki basharat di , ek Nabi saliheen mein se"
  37,113,Aur usey aur Ishaq ko barakat di. Ab in dono ki zurriyat mein se koi mohsin hai aur koi apne nafs par sareeh zulm karne wala hai
  37,114,Aur humne Moosa o Haroon par ehsan kiya
  37,115,Unko aur unki qaum ko karb-e-azeem( badi museebat) se nijaat di
  37,116,Unhein nusrat bakshi jiski wajah se wahi galib rahey
  37,117,Unko nihayat wazeh kitaab ata ki
  37,118,Unhein raah-e-raast dikhayi
  37,119,Aur baad ki nasalon mein unka zikr e khair baaqi rakkha
  37,120,Salaam hai Mossa aur Haroon par
  37,121,Hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza detay hain
  37,122,Dar haqeeqat woh hamare momin bandon mein se thay
  37,123,Aur Ilyas bhi yaqeenan mursaleen(messengers) mein se tha
  37,124,Yaad karo jab usne apni qaum se kaha tha ke “tum log darte nahin ho
  37,125,Kya tum BAAL ko pukarte ho aur ahsanul khaliqeen ko chodh dete ho
  37,126,Us Allah ko jo tumhara aur tumhare agle pichle aaba o ajdaad ka Rubb hai?”
  37,127,"Magar unhon ne usey jhutla diya, so ab yaqeenan woh saza ke liye pesh kiye janey waley hain"
  37,128,Bajuz un bandagaan e khuda ke jinko khaalis karliya gaya tha
  37,129,Aur Ilyas ka zikr e khair humne baad ki nasalon mein baaki rakkha
  37,130,Salaam hai Ilyas par
  37,131,Hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  37,132,Waqayi wo hamare momin bandon mein se tha
  37,133,Aur Lut bhi unhi logon mein se tha jo Rasool bana kar bheje gaye hain
  37,134,Yaad karo jab humne usko aur uske sab gar walon ko nijaat di
  37,135,Siwaye ek budiya ke jo peechey reh janey walon mein se thi
  37,136,Phir baaki sabko tehas nehas kardiya
  37,137,Aaj tum shab-o-roz unke ujday dayar (desolate habitations) par se guzarte ho
  37,138,Kya tumko aqal nahin aati
  37,139,Aur yaqeenan Yunus bhi Rasoolon mein se tha
  37,140,Yaad karo jab woh ek bhari kashti ki taraf bhaag nikla
  37,141,Phir quora andazi (cast lots) mein shareek hua aur usmein maath khayi (among the losers)
  37,142,Aakhir e kaar machli ne usey nigal liya aur woh malamat zada tha
  37,143,Ab agar woh tasbeeh karne walon mein se na hota to
  37,144,Roz-e-qayamat tak usi machli ke pait mein rehta
  37,145,Aakhir humne usey badi sakheem (bimar /ill) halat mein ek chatiyal zameen par phenk diya
  37,146,Aur uspar ek bail-daar darakht (a spreading plant of the gourd kind) uga diya
  37,147,Iske baad humne usey ek lakh ya us sey zayad logon ki taraf bheja
  37,148,Woh imaan laye aur humne ek waqt e khaas tak unhein baaqi rakkha
  37,149,"Phir zara in logon se pucho, kya (inke dil ko yeh baat lagti hai ke) tumhare Rubb ke liye to hon betiyan aur inke liye hon betay"
  37,150,Kya waqayi humne malaika (farishton) ko auratein banaya hai aur yeh aankhon dekhi baat keh rahey hain
  37,151,"Khoob sun rakkho, dar-asal yeh log apni mann ghadat se yeh baat kehte hain"
  37,152,"Ke Allah aulad rakhta hai, aur fil waqayi yeh jhootey hain"
  37,153,Kya Allah ne beton ke bajaye betiyan apne liye pasand karli
  37,154,"Tumhein kya ho gaya hai, kaise hukum laga rahey ho"
  37,155,Kya tumhein hosh nahin aata
  37,156,Ya phir tumhare paas apni in baaton ke liye koi saaf sanad (daleel) hai
  37,157,To lao apni woh kitaab agar tum sachhey ho
  37,158,"Inhon ne Allah aur malaika ke darmiyan nasab (kinship)ka rishta bana rakkha hai, halanke malaika khoob jaante hain ke yeh log mujrim ki haisiyat se pesh honay waley hain"
  37,159,(aur woh kehte hain ke) “Allah un sifaat se paak hai
  37,160,Jo uske khaalis bandon ke siwa dusre log uski taraf mansoob karte hain
  37,161,Pas tum aur tumhare yeh mabood
  37,162,Allah se kisi ko pher nahin sakte
  37,163,Magar sifr usko jo dozakh ki bhadakti hui aag mein jhulasne wala ho
  37,164,Aur hamara haal to yeh hai ke hum mein se har ek ka ek muqaam mukarrar hai
  37,165,Aur hum saff basta (in rows) khidmatgaar hain
  37,166,Tasbeeh karne waley hain.”
  37,167,Yeh log pehle to kaha karte thay
  37,168,Ke kaash hamare paas woh “Zikr” hota jo pichli qaumon ko mila tha
  37,169,To hum Allah ke cheedah (chune huey/chosen) banday hotay
  37,170,"Magar (jab woh aa gaya) to inhon ne uska inkar kardiya, ab ankareeb inhein (is rawish ka natija) maloom ho jayega"
  37,171,Apne bheje huey bandon se hum pehle hi waada kar chuke hain
  37,172,Ke yaqeenan unki madad ki jayegi
  37,173,Aur hamara lashkar hi gaalib hokar rahega
  37,174,Pas (aey Nabi) zara kuch muddat tak inhein inke haal par chodh do
  37,175,"Aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud bhi dekh lengey"
  37,176,Kya yeh hamare azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahey hain
  37,177,Jab woh inke sehan (maidan/open space) mein aa utrega woh din un logon ke liye bahut bura hoga jinhein mutanabbeh (warn) kiya ja chuka hai
  37,178,Pas zara inhein kuch muddat ke liye chodh do
  37,179,"Aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud dekh lenge"
  37,180,"Paak hai tera Rubb, izzat ka maalik, un tamaam baaton se jo yeh log bana rahey hain"
  37,181,Aur salaam hai mursalin (messengers) par
  37,182,Aur saari taarif Allah Rabbul Aalameen hi ke liye hai
  38,1,"Saad, kasam hai naseehat bharey Quran ki"
  38,2,"Balke yahi log, jinhon ne maanney se inkar kiya hai, sakht takabbur aur zid mein mubtila hain"
  38,3,"Insey pehle hum aisi kitni hi qaumon ko halaak kar chuke hain (aur jab unki shamat aayi hai) to woh cheekh utthey hain, magar woh waqt bachne ka nahin hota"
  38,4,"In logon ko is baat par bada taajub hua ke ek darane wala khud inhi mein se aa gaya, munkireen kehne lagey ke “yeh saahir(sorcerer) hai, sakht jhoota hai"
  38,5,Kya isney saarey khudaon ki jagah bas ek hi khuda bana dala? Yeh to badi ajeeb baat hai”
  38,6,Aur sardaran e qaum yeh kehte huey nikal gaye ke “ chalo aur dat-tey raho apne maboodon ki ibadat par. Yeh baat to kisi aur hi garaz se kahi ja rahi hai
  38,7,Yeh baat humne zamana e qareeb ki millat mein kisi se nahin suni. Yeh kuch nahin hai magar ek man-ghadat baat
  38,8,"Kya hamarey darmiyan bas yahi ek shaks reh gaya tha jispar Allah ka zikr nazil kardiya gaya?”Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh mere “Zikr” par shakk kar rahey hain , aur yeh saari baatein isliye kar rahey hain ke inhon ne mere azaab ka maza chakkha nahin hai"
  38,9,Kya tere daata (great Bestower) aur gaalib parwardigar ki rehmat ke khazane inke kabze mein hain
  38,10,Kya yeh aasmaan o zameen aur inke darmiyan ki cheezon ke maalik hain? Accha to yeh aalam e asbaab ki bulandiyon par chadh kar dekhein
  38,11,Yeh to jatthon (armies) mein se ek choota sa jattha (army) hai jo isi jagah shikhast(suffer defeat) khane wala hai
  38,12,"Insey pehle Nooh ki qaum, aur Aad, aur mekhon (tent-pegs/stakes) wala Firoun"
  38,13,"Aur Samood, aur qaum e Lut, aur aika waley jhutla chuke hain. Jatthay woh thay"
  38,14,Unmein se har ek ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya aur meri uqubat ka faisla (decree of chastisement )uspar chaspan ho kar raha
  38,15,Yeh log bhi bas ek dhamake ke muntazir hain jiske baad koi dusra dhamaka na hoga
  38,16,"Aur yeh kehte hain ke aey hamare Rubb, yaum ul hisaab(hisab ke din) se pehle hi hamara hissa humein jaldi se dey dey"
  38,17,"(Aey Nabi), sabr karo un baaton par jo yeh log banate hain, aur inke saamne hamare banday Dawood ka qissa bayan karo jo badi quwaton ka maalik tha. Har maamle mein Allah ki taraf rujoo karne wala tha"
  38,18,Humne pahadon ko uske saath musakkhar kar rakkha tha ke subah o shaam woh uske saath tasbeeh karte thay
  38,19,Parindey simat aate aur sabke sab uski tasbeeh ki taraf mutawajjeh ho jatey thay
  38,20,"Humne uski sultanat mazboot kardi thi, usko hikmat ata ki thi aur faislay-kun baat kehne ki salahiyat bakshi thi"
  38,21,Phir tumhein kuch khabar pahunchi hai un muqaddame walon ki jo deewaar chadh kar uske baala khaane(private chambers) mein ghus aaye thay
  38,22,"Jab woh Dawood ke paas pahunche to woh unhein dekh kar ghabra gaya, unhon ne kaha “dariye nahin, hum do fareeq muqaddama hain jin mein se ek ne dusre par zyadati ki hai. Aap hamare darmiyan theek theek haqq ke saath faisla kardijiye, be-insafi na kijiye aur humein raah e raast bataiye"
  38,23,"Yeh meri bhai hai ,iske paas ninanve (ninety nine) dumbiyan(ewes) hai aur mere paas sirf ek hi dumbi (ewe) hai , isne mujhse kaha ke yeh ek dumbi bhi mere hawale karde aur isne guftagu mein mujhe daba liya”"
  38,24,"Dawood ne jawab diya: “is shaks ne apni dumbiyon (ewes) ke saath teri dumbi mila lene ka mutalaba karke yaqeenan tujhpar zulm kiya, aur waqiya yeh hai ke mil-jhul kar saath rehne waley log aksar ek dusre par zyadatiyan karte rehte hain, bas wahi log is se bachey huey hain jo iman rakhte hain aur amal e saleh karte hain, aur aisey log kam hi hain.” (Yeh baat kehte kehte) Dawood samajh gaya ke yeh to humne dar-asal iski aazmaish ki hai, chunanche usne apne Rubb se maafi maangi aur sajde mein gir gaya aur rujoo karliya"
  38,25,Tab humne iska woh kasoor maaf kiya aur yaqeenan hamare haan uske liye taqarrub ka muqaam aur behtar anjaam hai
  38,26,"(Humne ussey kaha) “Aey dawood, humne tujhey zameen mein khalifa banaya hai, lihaza tu logon ke darmiyan haqq ke saath hukumat kar, aur khwaish e nafs ki pairwi na kar ke woh tujhey Allah ki raah se bhatka degi. Jo log Allah ki raah se bhatakte hain yaqeenan unke liye sakht saza hai ke woh yaum ul hisaab ko bhool gaye.”"
  38,27,"Humne is aasmaan aur zameen ko, aur is duniya ko jo inke darmiyan hai , fizool paida nahin kardiya hai, yeh to un logon ka gumaan hai jinhon ne kufr kiya hai aur aisey kaafiron ke liye barbadi hai jahannum ki aag se"
  38,28,Kya hum un logon ko jo iman laatey hain aur neik aamaal karte hain aur unko jo zameen mein fasad karne waley hain yaksan kardein? Kya muttaqiyon ko hum faajiron(wicked) jaisa kardein
  38,29,Yeh ek badi barakat wali kitaab hai jo (aey Muhammad) humne tumhari taraf nazil ki hai taa-ke yeh log iski aayat par gaur karein aur aqal o fikr rakhne wale issey sabaq lein
  38,30,"Aur Dawood ko humne Sulaiman (jaisa beta) ata kiya, behtareen banda, kasrat se apne Rubb ki taraf rujoo karne wala"
  38,31,Kaabil e zikr hai woh mauqa jab shaam ke waqt us ke saamne khoob sidhey (well-trained) huey tez-rau(running) ghoday (horses) pesh kiye gaye
  38,32,To usne kaha “maine is maal ki muhabbat apne Rubb ki yaad ki wajah se ikhtiyar ki hai” yahan tak ke jab woh ghoday (horses) nigaah se ojhal ho gaye
  38,33,"To (usne hukum diya ke) inhein mere paas wapas laao, phir laga unki pindliyon (legs) aur gardano (necks) par haath pherne"
  38,34,Aur (dekho ke) Sulaiman ko bhi humne aazmaish mein daala aur uski kursi par ek jasad (mere body/body without life) laa kar daal diya phir usne rujoo kiya
  38,35,"Aur kaha ke “aey mere Rubb , mujhey maaf karde aur mujhey woh baadshahi de jo mere baad kisi ke liye sazawar na ho, beshak tu hi asal daata hai”"
  38,36,Tab humne uske liye hawa ko musakkhar kardiya jo uske hukum se narmi ke saath chalti thi jidhar woh chahta tha
  38,37,"Aur shayateen ko musakkhar kardiya, har tarah ke meimaar(builders) aur gotakhor (divers)"
  38,38,Aur dusre jo paband e salasil thay(bound with chains)
  38,39,"(humne ussey kaha) “ yeh hamari bakshish hai, tujhey ikhtiyar hai jisey chahe de aur jissey chahe rok le, koi hisaab nahin”"
  38,40,Yaqeenan uske liye hamare haan taqarrub ka muqaam aur behtar anjaam hai
  38,41,"Aur hamare banday Ayub ka zikar karo, jab usne apne Rubb ko pukara ke shaytaan ne mujhey sakht takleef aur azaab mein daal diya hai"
  38,42,"(Humne usey hukum diya) apna paaon (leg) zameen par maar, yeh hai thanda pani nahane ke liya aur peene ke liye"
  38,43,"Humne usey uske ahal o ayaal wapas diye aur unke saath utnay hi aur, apni taraf se rehmat ke taur par, aur aqal o fikar rakhne walon ke liye dars ke taur par"
  38,44,"(Aur humne issey kaha) tinkon ka ek mutta lay (bundle of rushes) aur ussey maar de, apni kasam na todh, humne usey saabir paya, behtareen banda, apne Rubb ki taraf bahut rujoo karne wala"
  38,45,"Aur hamare bandon , Ibrahim aur Ishaq aur Yaqub ka zikar karo badi quwwat e amail rakhne wale aur deedhawar (strength and vision)log thay"
  38,46,"Humne unko ek khaalis siffat ki bina par barguzida kiya tha, aur woh daar-e-aakhirat ki yaad thi"
  38,47,Yaqeenan hamare haan unka shumaar chunay huey neik ashkhaas(excellent ones) mein hai
  38,48,"Aur Ismail aur Al-yasa(Elisha) aur Zulkifl ka zikr karo, yeh sab neik logon mein se thay"
  38,49,Yeh ek zikar tha. (Ab suno ke) muttaqi logon ke liye yaqeenan behtareen thikana hai
  38,50,Hamesha rehne wali jannatein jinke darwaze unke liye khuley hongey
  38,51,"Unmein woh takiye lagaye baithay hongey, khoob khoob fawake aur mashroobat (abundant fruit and drinks) talab kar rahey hongey"
  38,52,Aur unke paas sharmili humsin biwiyan hongi
  38,53,Yeh woh chezein hain jinhein hisaab ke din ata karne ka tumse wada kiya ja raha hai
  38,54,Yeh hamara rizq hai jo kabhi khatam honaywala nahin
  38,55,Yeh to hai muttaqiyon ka anjaam aur sarkashon ke liye badhtareen (evil) thikana hai
  38,56,Jahannum jismein woh jhulse jayenge. Bahut hi buri qayamgaah
  38,57,"Yeh hai unke liye, pas woh maza chakhein khautley (boiling) huey pani aur peep lahu (pus)"
  38,58,Aur isi qisam ki dusri talkhiyon ka
  38,59,"(woh jahannum ki taraf apne pairawon ko aatey dekh kar aapas mein kahenge) “Yeh ek lashkar tumhare paas ghusa chala aa raha hai, koi khushamadeed (welcome) inke liye nahin hai, yeh aag mein jhulasne waley hain”"
  38,60,"Woh unko jawab denge “ nahin balke tum hi jhulse ja rahe ho, koi khair maqdam tumhare liye nahin. Tumhi to yeh anjaam hamare aagey laye ho. Kaisi buri hai yeh jaaye qaraar”"
  38,61,"Phir woh kahenge “Aey hamare Rubb, jisne humein is anjaam ko pahunchane ka bandobast kiya usko dozakh ka dohra azaab de”"
  38,62,"Aur woh aapas mein kahenge “kya baat hai, hum un logon ko kahin nahin dekhte jinehin hum duniya mein bura samajte thay"
  38,63,"Hunme yunhi unka mazaaq bana liya tha, ya woh kahin nazaron se ojhal hain?”"
  38,64,"Beshak yeh baat sacchi hai, ehle dozakh mein yahi kuch jhagde honay waley hain"
  38,65,"(Aey Nabi) insey kaho, “ main to bas khabardar kardene wala hoon. Koi haqeeqi mabood nahin magar Allah, jo yakta hai, sab par gaalib"
  38,66,"Aasmaano aur zameen ka maalik aur un saari cheezon ka maalik jo inke darmiyan hain, zabardast aur darguzar karne wala”"
  38,67,Insey kaho “ yeh ek badi khabar hai
  38,68,Jisko sunkar tum mooh pherte ho”
  38,69,(Insey kaho) “Mujhey us waqt ki koi khabar na thi jab mala-e-aala (high council) mein jhagda ho raha tha
  38,70,Mujhko to wahee (revelation/inspiration) ke zariye se yeh baatein sirf isliye batayi jaati hain ke main khula khula khabardar karne wala hoon”
  38,71,Jab tere Rubb ne farishton se kaha “main mitti se ek bashar banane wala hoon
  38,72,Phir jab main usey puri tarah bana doon aur usmein apni rooh phoonk doon to tum uske aagey sajde mein gir jao”
  38,73,Is hukum ke mutaabiq farishtey sab ke sab sajde mein gir gaye
  38,74,Magar Iblis ne apni badayi ka ghamand kiya aur woh kaafiron mein se ho gaya
  38,75,"Rubb ne farmaya “Aey Iblis, tujhey kya cheez usko sajda karne se maanay hui jisey maine apne dono haathon se banaya hai? Tu bada ban raha hai ya tu hai hi kuch unchey darje ki hastiyon mein se?”"
  38,76,"Usne jawab diya “main ussey behtar hoon , aapne mujhko aag se paida kiya hai aur isko mitti se”"
  38,77,"Farmaya “ accha to yahan se nikal ja , tu mardood hai"
  38,78,Aur tere upar yaum ul jaza tak meri laanat hai”
  38,79,"Woh bola “ aey mere Rubb , yeh baat hai to phir mujhey us waqt tak ke liye mohlat dey dey jab yeh log dobara uthaye jayenge”"
  38,80,"Farmaya, “accha tujhey us roz tak ki mohlat hai"
  38,81,Jiska waqt mujhey maloom hai”
  38,82,"Usne kaha “ teri izzat ki kasam, main in sab logon ko behka kar rahunga"
  38,83,Bajuz tere un bandon ke jinhein tu nay khaalis karliya hai”
  38,84,"Farmaya “to haqq yeh hai, aur main haqq hi kaha karta hoon"
  38,85,Ke main jahannum ko tujhse aur un sab logon se bhar dunga jo in Insano mein se teri pairwi karenge”
  38,86,"(Aey Nabi) insey kehdo ke main is tableeg par tumse koi ajar nahin maangta, aur na main banawati logon mein se hoon"
  38,87,Yeh to ek naseehat hai tamam jahaan walon ke liye
  38,88,Aur thodi muddat hi guzaregi ke tumhein iska haal khud maaloom ho jayega
  39,1,Is kitaab ka nuzul Allah zabardast aur dana (hikmat wala/full of Wisdom) ki taraf se hai
  39,2,"(Aey Muhammad) yeh kitab humne tumhari taraf barhaqq nazil ki hai, lihaza tum Allah hi ki bandagi karo deen ko usi ke liye khalis karte huey"
  39,3,"Khabardar, deen e khalis Allah ka haqq hai.Rahey woh log jinhon ne uske siwa dusre sarparst bana rakkhe hain (aur apne is fail ki taujeeh yeh karte hain ke) hum to unki ibadat sirf is liye karte hain ke woh Allah tak hamari rasayi karadein (bring us nearer to Allah).Allah yaqeenan unke darmiyan un tamaam baaton ka faisla kardega jin mein woh ikhtilaf kar rahey hain. Allah kisi aisey shaks ko hidayat nahin deta jo jhoota aur munkir e haqq ho"
  39,4,"Agar Allah kisi ko beta banana chahta to apni makhlooq mein se jisko chahta barguzida kar leta, Paak hai woh issey (ke koi uska beta ho), woh Allah hai akela aur sab par gaalib"
  39,5,"Usne aasmano aur zameen ko barhaqq paida kiya hai. Wahi din par raat aur raat par din ko lapeit-ta hai.Usi ne Suraj aur Chand ko is tarah musakkhar kar rakkha hai ke har ek ek waqt e muqarrar tak chale ja raha hai. Jaan rakkho, woh zabardast hai aur darguzar karne wala hai"
  39,6,"Usi ne tumko ek jaan se paida kiya, phir wahi hai jisne us jaan se iska joda banaya aur usi ne tumhare liye maweshiyon mein se aath (eight) nar o maada paida kiye. Woh tumhari Maaon (mothers) ke paithon mein teen teen tareekh (andherey) paradon ke andar tumhein ek ke baad ek shakal deta chala jaata hai. Yahi Allah (jiske yeh kaam hain) tumhara Rubb hai, baadshahi usi ki hai, koi mabood uske siwa nahin hai, phir tum kidhar se phiraye jaa rahe ho"
  39,7,"Agar tum kufr karo to Allah tumse be niyaz hai, lekin woh apne bandon ke liye kufr ko pasand nahin karta. Aur agar tum shukar karo to usey woh tumhare liye pasand karta hai. Koi bojh uthane wala kisi dusre ka bojh na uthayega.Aakhir e kaar tum sab ko apne Rubb ki taraf palatna hai, phir woh tumhein bata dega ke tum kya karte rahe ho, woh to dilon ka haal tak jaanta hai"
  39,8,"Insaan par jab koi aafat aati hai to woh apne Rubb ki taraf rujoo (return) karke usey pukarta hai, phir jab uska Rubb usey apni niyamat se nawaz deta hai to woh us musibat ko bhool jaata hai jispar woh pehle pukar raha tha aur dusron ko Allah ka humsar thehrata hai taa-ke uski raah se gumraah karey. (Aey Nabi) ussey kaho ke thode din apne kufr se lutf utha le, yaqeenan tu dozakh mein jaane wala hai"
  39,9,"(kya is shaks ki rawish behtar hai ya us shaks ki) jo mutii-e-farmaan hai, raat ki ghadiyon mein khada rehta hai aur sajdey karta hai, aakhirat se darta aur apne Rubb ki rehmat se umeed lagata hai? In se pucho, kya jaanne waley aur na jaanne waley dono kabhi yaksan ho sakte hain? Naseehat to aqal rakhne waley hi qabool karte hain"
  39,10,"(Aey Nabi) kaho ke aey mere bandon jo imaan laye ho, apne Rubb se daro. Jin logon ne is duniya mein neik rawayya ikhtiyar kiya hai unke liye bhalayi hai. Aur khuda ki zameen waseeh hai, sabr karne walon ko to unka ajar be-hisaab diya jayega"
  39,11,"(Aey Nabi) insey kaho, mujhey hukum diya gaya hai ke deen ko Allah ke liye khaalis karke uski bandagi karoon"
  39,12,Aur mujhey hukum diya gaya hai ke sabse pehle main khud muslim banoon
  39,13,"Kaho, agar mein apne Rubb ki naafarmaani karoon to mujhey ek badey din ke azaab ka khauf hai"
  39,14,Kehdo ke main to apne deen ko Allah ke liye khalis karke usi ki bandagi karunga
  39,15,"Tum uske siwa jis jis ki bandagi karna chaho karte raho. Kaho asal diwaliye (losers) to wahi hain jinhon ne qayamat ke roz apne aap ko aur apne ahal-o-aayal ko ghaatey(loss) mein daal diya. khoob sun rakkho, yahi khula diwala (loss) hai"
  39,16,"Unpar aag ki chatriyan upar se bhi chayi hongi aur nichey se bhi. Yeh woh anjaam hai jissey Allah apne bandon ko darata hai, pas aey mere bandon, mere gazab se bacho"
  39,17,Ba-khilaf iske jin logon ne tagut(false gods) ki bandagi se ijtinab kiya aur Allah ki taraf rujoo karliya unke liye khush khabri hai .Pas (Aey Nabi) basharat dedo mere un bandon ko
  39,18,"Jo baat ko gaur se sunte hain aur uske behtareen pehlu ki pairwi karte hain, yeh woh log hain jinko Allah ne hidayat bakshi hai aur yahi daanishmand (with understanding) hain"
  39,19,(Aey Nabi) us shaks ko kaun bacha sakta hai jispar azaab ka faisla chaspan ho chuka ho? Kya tum usey bacha sakte ho jo aag mein gir chuka ho
  39,20,"Albatta jo log apne Rubb se darr kar rahey unke liye buland imaratein hain manzil par manzil bani hui jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi. yeh Allah ka waada hai, Allah kabhi apne waade ki khilaf warzi nahin karta"
  39,21,"Kya tum nahin dekhte ke Allah ne aasmaan se pani barsaya, phir usko soton aur chashmon (springs and streams )aur daryaon ki shakal mein zameen ke andar jaari kiya. Phir is pani ke zariye se woh tarah tarah ki khetiyan nikalta hai jinki kismein mukhtalif hain, phir woh khetiyan pak kar sukh jaati hai, phir tum dekhte ho ke woh zard (yellow) padh gayi, phir aakhir e kaar Allah unko bhus bana deta hai. Dar haqeeqat is mein ek sabak hai aqal rakhne waalon ke liye"
  39,22,Ab kya woh shaks jiska seena Allah ne Islam ke liye khol diya aur woh apne Rubb ki taraf se ek roshni par chal raha hai (us shaks ki tarah ho sakta hai jisne in baaton se koi sabaq na liya)? Tabahi hai un logon ke liye jinke dil Allah ki naseehat se aur zyada sakht ho gaye. Woh khuli gumrahi mein padey huey hain
  39,23,"Allah ne behtareen kalaam utara hai, ek aisi kitaab jiske tamaam ajzah humrang hain aur jis mein baar baar mazameen(contents) dohraye gaye hain, usey sunkar un logon ke rongtey khade ho jatey hain jo apne Rubb se darne waley hain, aur phir unke jism aur unke dil naram hokar Allah ke zikr ki taraf raagib ho jatey hain. Yeh Allah ki hidayat hai jissey woh raah e raast par le aata hai jisey chahta hai aur jisey Allah hi hidayat na de uske liye phir koi haadi (guide) nahin hai"
  39,24,Ab us shaks ki bad-haali ka tum kya andaza kar sakte ho jo qayamat ke roz azaab ki sakht maar apne mooh par lega? Aisey zaalimon se to kehdiya jayega ke ab chakko maza us kamayi ka jo tum karte rahey thay
  39,25,Insey pehle bhi bahut se log isi tarah jhutla chuke hain. Aakhir unpar azaab aisey rukh se aaya jidhar unka khayal bhi na ja sakta tha
  39,26,"Phir Allah ne unko duniya hi ki zindgai mein ruswayi ka maza chakhaya, aur aakhirat ka azaab to issey shadeed tarr hai, kaash yeh log jaante"
  39,27,Humne is Quran mein logon ko tarah tarah ki misalein di hain ke yeh hosh mein aayein
  39,28,"Aisa Quraan jo arabi zubaan mein hai, jis mein koi tedh (croockedness) nahin hai, taa-ke yeh burey anjaam se bachein"
  39,29,"Allah ek misaal deta hai ek shaks to woh hai jiski milkiyat mein bahut se kaj khulq (several quarrelsome masters) aaqaa shareek hain jo usey apni apni taraf khinchte hain aur dusra shaks poora ka poora ek hi aaqaa ka gulaam hai. Kya in dono ka haal yaksan ho sakta hai? Alhamdulillah, magar aksar log nadaani mein padey huye hain"
  39,30,(Aey Nabi) tumhein bhi marna hai aur in logon ko bhi marna hai
  39,31,Aakhir e kaar qayamat ke roz tum sab apne Rubb ke huzur apna apna muqaddama pesh karogey